This is a build of Google Chromium (the open source project behind Google Chrome) for Intel Macs. It was built on 21 March 2009 at around 11:30pm on a MacBook4,1 from the SVN Source tree, so it's the most current as of that date.

This is far from even being a beta, so expect bugs.
